<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧٥ - حَدَّثَنِي أَبِي، عَنِ الْأَصْمَعِيِّ،<span class="c5"> أَنَّهُ سَمِعَ امْرَأَةً مِنْ أَهْلِ الْبَادِيَةِ تَقُولُ لِابْنٍ لَهَا:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الرجز]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فِدَاكَ أَهْلُ الْحِيرَةِ ... فِي الشَّامِ وَالْجَزِيرَةْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَشَرْقِ عَمِيرَةَ ... وَمُضَرَ الْكَبِيرَةْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمِنْ أُنَاسٍ جِيرَةْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> وَسَمِعْتُهَا تَقُولُ لَهُ:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أُعِيذُهُ بِالْأَعْلَى ... مِنْ شَرِّ كُلِّ أُنْثَى<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مُرْضِعَةٍ أَوْ حُبْلَى ... أَوْ أَيِّمٍ حِينَ تُرْجَى<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَوْ عَاقِرٍ تَمَنَّى ... تَمَرَاتِهَا تَرَدَّى<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فِي بَحْرِهَا يُؤَدَّى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>